 {"id":"frankenpandas-fd90.53","title":"test(readme): SqlColumnSchema declared_type/autoincrement/default_value field coverage","description":"SqlColumnSchema has 7 fields total. Existing tests exercise name, nullable, primary_key_ordinal. The other 3 (declared_type, default_value, autoincrement) are uncovered.

